<text><body>
<lb n="0030c10"/>
<milestone unit="juan" n="1"/>
<lb n="0030c11"/>
<lb n="0030c12"/>
<lb n="0030c13"/><head type="no">No. 1040</head>
<lb n="0030c14"/><juan fun="open" n="001"><mulu type="卷" n="001"/><jhead><note n="0030012" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">【原】麗本，【甲】三十帖策子第五</note>金剛頂降三世大儀軌法王教中
<lb n="0030c15"/>觀自在菩薩心真言一切如來蓮
<lb n="0030c16"/>花大曼<note n="0030013" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">拏&CB00256;＝荼羅【甲】＊</note><app n="0030013"><lem>拏&CB00256;</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">荼羅</rdg></app>品<note n="0030014" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔一卷〕－【甲】</note><app n="0030014"><lem>一卷</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app></jhead></juan>
<lb n="0030c17"/>
<lb n="0030c18"/><byline type="Translator"><note n="0030015" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔開府…智〕三十三字－【甲】</note><app n="0030015" word-count="33"><lem>開府儀同三司特進試鴻臚卿肅國
<lb n="0030c19"/>公食邑三千戶賜紫贈司空諡大鑒
<lb n="0030c20"/>正號大廣智</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>大興善寺三藏沙<note n="0030016" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">門＋（大廣智）【甲】</note><app n="0030016"><lem>門</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">門大廣智</rdg></app>
<lb n="0030c21"/>不空奉　詔譯</byline>
<lb n="0030c22"/><div1 type="jing"><p>爾時觀自在菩薩摩訶薩。白佛言。世尊我欲
<lb n="0030c23"/>於此降三世儀軌法王會中說自心真言。世
<lb n="0030c24"/>尊若纔稱<note n="0030017" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">說＝誦【甲】＊</note><app n="0030017"><lem>說</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">誦</rdg></app>一切如來。三昧現前一切怖畏
<lb n="0030c25"/>厄難災障。及諸病惱皆得<note n="0030018" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">消＝銷【甲】</note><app n="0030018"><lem>消</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">銷</rdg></app>滅</p>
<lb n="0030c26"/><p>爾時薄伽梵。告觀自在菩薩言。善哉善哉汝
<lb n="0030c27"/>應善說。時觀自在菩薩摩訶薩。承佛聖旨即
<lb n="0030c28"/>說自心真言曰</p>
<lb n="0030c29"/><p type="dharani">阿嚕<note n="0030019" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（禮迦…引）十字＝（力）一字【甲】</note><app n="0030019" word-count="10"><lem>禮迦<note place="inline">半</note>娑&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合引</note>賀<note place="inline">引</note></lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">力</rdg></app></p>
<pb ed="T" id="T20.1040.0031a" n="0031a"/>
<lb n="0031a01"/><p>適說此心真言時。一切如來從本剎土。雲集
<lb n="0031a02"/>蘇<note n="0031001" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">迷＝彌【甲】</note><app n="0031001"><lem>迷</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">彌</rdg></app>盧頂毘盧遮那大會之中。圍遶觀自在
<lb n="0031a03"/>菩薩摩訶薩復說自心真言大曼<anchor id="fxT20p0031a01"/>拏&CB00256;</p>
<lb n="0031a04"/><lg><l>院位擘方設</l><l>內四角<note n="0031002" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">四＝向【甲】</note><app n="0031002"><lem>四</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">向</rdg></app>門</l>
<lb n="0031a05"/><l>善度最中央</l><l>井形<note n="0031003" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">拼＝抨【甲】</note><app n="0031003"><lem>拼</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">抨</rdg></app>四道</l>
<lb n="0031a06"/><l>顯成於八位</l><l>分為八葉花</l>
<lb n="0031a07"/><l>是色應用朱</l><l>中臺觀自在</l>
<lb n="0031a08"/><l>於彼一一葉</l><l>圖畫大覺形</l>
<lb n="0031a09"/><l>中院不為門</l><l>內外八線道</l>
<lb n="0031a10"/><l>微妙建立已</l><l>阿闍梨當入</l>
<lb n="0031a11"/><l>應對曼<anchor id="fxT20p0031a02"/>拏&CB00256;</l><l>結大蓮花契</l>
<lb n="0031a12"/><l>端身定支節</l><l>住於三摩地</l>
<lb n="0031a13"/><l>次結盎俱施</l><l>奉請於聖者</l>
<lb n="0031a14"/><l>若一切有情</l><l>入此曼<anchor id="fxT20p0031a03"/>拏&CB00256;</l>
<lb n="0031a15"/><l>雖處於凡位</l><l>貪嗔罪垢滅</l>
<lb n="0031a16"/><l>猶如於蓮花</l><l>不為水所著</l>
<lb n="0031a17"/><l>勝生亦如是</l><l>不為欲所染</l></lg>
<lb n="0031a18"/><p>阿闍梨即以大蓮花印。屈進力度如鉤。請<note n="0031004" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">觀＋（世）【甲】</note><app n="0031004"><lem>觀</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">觀世</rdg></app>
<lb n="0031a19"/>自在菩薩。蓮花鉤真言曰</p>
<lb n="0031a20"/><p type="dharani">唵<note place="inline"><note n="0031005" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">引＝一【甲】＊</note><app n="0031005"><lem>引</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">一</rdg></app></note>摩訶<note place="inline"><note n="0031006" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">引＋（二）【甲】</note><app n="0031006"><lem>引</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">引二</rdg></app></note>跛<note n="0031007" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">娜＝納【甲】＊</note><app n="0031007"><lem>娜</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">納</rdg></app>摩<note place="inline">二<note n="0031008" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">合＋（三）【甲】</note><app n="0031008"><lem>合</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">合三</rdg></app></note><note n="0031009" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">吽＋（四）細註【甲】</note><app n="0031009"><lem>吽</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">吽<note place="inline">四</note></rdg></app><note n="0031010" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">惹＋（入五）細註【甲】</note><app n="0031010"><lem>惹</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">惹<note place="inline">入五</note></rdg></app></p>
<lb n="0031a21"/><p>即時觀自在菩薩便至道場現微妙色身。或
<lb n="0031a22"/>放光明。阿闍梨次當如法引弟子入。是諸弟
<lb n="0031a23"/>子應著白衣。復以白繒<note n="0031011" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">掩＝帕【甲】</note><app n="0031011"><lem>掩</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">帕</rdg></app>覆其<note n="0031012" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">服＝眼【甲】</note><app n="0031012"><lem>服</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">眼</rdg></app>。又以淨
<lb n="0031a24"/>帛纏繫其頭。既引入已而<anchor id="fxT20p0031a04"/>說偈<note n="0031013" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">言＝曰【甲】＊</note><app n="0031013"><lem>言</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">曰</rdg></app></p>
<lb n="0031a25"/><lg><l>猶如於蓮花</l><l>不為水所著</l>
<lb n="0031a26"/><l>勝生亦如是</l><l>不為諸欲染</l></lg>
<lb n="0031a27"/><p>即應在手授與弟子蓮花。右手授與念珠。又
<lb n="0031a28"/><anchor id="fxT20p0031a05"/>說偈<anchor id="fxT20p0031a06"/>言</p>
<lb n="0031a29"/><lg><l>諸佛大蓮花</l><l>於諸曼<anchor id="fxT20p0031a07"/>拏&CB00256;</l>
<pb ed="T" id="T20.1040.0031b" n="0031b"/>
<lb n="0031b01"/><l>最為其上首</l><l>常須分別思</l>
<lb n="0031b02"/><l>身奉觀自在</l></lg>
<lb n="0031b03"/><p>然後教印及三摩地門</p></div1>
<lb n="0031b04"/><div1 type="pin"><mulu type="品" level="1" n="2" label="心真言蓮花曼拏[打-丁+羅]品"/><head>心真言蓮花曼<anchor id="fxT20p0031b01"/>拏&CB00256;品</head>
<lb n="0031b05"/><p>復<note n="0031014" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">次＝以【甲】</note><app n="0031014"><lem>次</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">以</rdg></app>如前建立曼<anchor id="fxT20p0031b02"/>拏&CB00256;。行者應坐中臺之
<lb n="0031b06"/>上。入一切如來開敷蓮花三摩地。誦一洛叉
<lb n="0031b07"/>即得觀自在身</p></div1>
<lb n="0031b08"/><div1 type="pin"><mulu type="品" level="1" n="3" label="心真言三昧耶曼拏[打-丁+羅]品"/><head>心真言<note n="0031015" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔三昧耶〕－【甲】</note><app n="0031015"><lem>三昧耶</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>曼<anchor id="fxT20p0031b03"/>拏&CB00256;品</head>
<lb n="0031b09"/><p>復以如前建立曼<anchor id="fxT20p0031b04"/>拏&CB00256;。應取一千蓮花。一花
<lb n="0031b10"/>一誦安中臺以為奉獻。然後引弟子入告三
<lb n="0031b11"/>昧耶言<note place="inline"><note n="0031016" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">謂＝為【甲】＊</note><app n="0031016"><lem>謂</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">為</rdg></app>諸欲清淨誓也</note></p></div1>
<lb n="0031b12"/><div1 type="pin"><mulu type="品" level="1" n="4" label="羯磨曼拏[打-丁+羅]品"/><head>羯磨曼<anchor id="fxT20p0031b05"/>拏&CB00256;品</head>
<lb n="0031b13"/><p>復次如前建立曼<anchor id="fxT20p0031b06"/>拏&CB00256;。以四種供養。復次成
<lb n="0031b14"/>就像法。於清淨絹&CB00626;上。畫觀自在菩薩。坐蘇
<lb n="0031b15"/>彌盧頂八佛圍遶。起白月一日於此像前。一
<lb n="0031b16"/>切時無間斷入三摩地念誦。乃至畫像放光。
<lb n="0031b17"/>於光明中流出觀自在菩薩及諸如來。入行
<lb n="0031b18"/>者眉間灌頂之處。堅固而住。即時行者體同
<lb n="0031b19"/>觀自在。剎那頃便見極樂世界。一切眾生皆
<lb n="0031b20"/>見去時壽命無量</p>
<lb n="0031b21"/><p>我今又說成就之法。誦一洛叉。一切蓋障皆
<lb n="0031b22"/>得清淨。誦二洛叉。所有五無間等一切諸罪
<lb n="0031b23"/>盡滅無餘。誦三洛叉。一切福德來集。一切
<lb n="0031b24"/>如來等備具。一切成智現前</p>
<lb n="0031b25"/><p>復次若結大印<note place="inline"><anchor id="fxT20p0031b07"/>謂五相成<note n="0031017" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">就＝身【甲】</note><app n="0031017"><lem>就</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">身</rdg></app></note>誦洛叉數。經夜無限
<lb n="0031b26"/>念誦。比至晨朝一切如來入行者心。即體同
<lb n="0031b27"/>如來。若入於口即<note n="0031018" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔體〕－【甲】</note><app n="0031018"><lem>體</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>同觀自在</p>
<lb n="0031b28"/><p>復次成就事業。誦一遍護身。兩遍護他及城
<lb n="0031b29"/>邑聚落。三遍<note n="0031019" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">即＝則【甲】</note><app n="0031019"><lem>即</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">則</rdg></app>能成辦一切事業。若阿尾捨
<pb ed="T" id="T20.1040.0031c" n="0031c"/>
<lb n="0031c01"/>應燒檀香<note place="inline">加持八百遍爐中燒薰支分</note>若息諸鬼魅者。加<note n="0031020" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">呬＝紇【甲】</note><app n="0031020"><lem>呬</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">紇</rdg></app>
<lb n="0031c02"/>唎<note n="0031021" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔二合〕－【甲】</note><app n="0031021"><lem><note place="inline">二合</note></lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>字誦之。令一切有情<note n="0031022" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（隨）＋順【甲】</note><app n="0031022"><lem>順</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">隨順</rdg></app>。加持金剛花
<lb n="0031c03"/>與之<note place="inline">赤花代之</note>令惡心不動。以<note n="0031023" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔白〕－【甲】</note><app n="0031023"><lem>白</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>土止息之<note place="inline">真言首加書朱
<lb n="0031c04"/>書之名後即卷置一瓶之中以白土實<note n="0031024" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">之＋（覆）【甲】</note><app n="0031024"><lem>之</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">之覆</rdg></app>安於一<note n="0031025" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">坑＝瓶【甲】</note><app n="0031025"><lem>坑</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">瓶</rdg></app>之中<note n="0031026" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">後＝又【甲】</note><app n="0031026"><lem>後</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">又</rdg></app>土填之想室彼<note n="0031027" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">兌＝瓮【甲】</note><app n="0031027"><lem>兌</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">瓮</rdg></app>即安須彌山於其上下亦得耳</note>
<lb n="0031c05"/>令悉底利敬愛。加持蘇末那花。與之伏從。又
<lb n="0031c06"/>欲令一切禽獸隨處不動轉白芥子令一切禽
<lb n="0031c07"/>獸不能動。加持白芥子遙向擲之。欲有所示
<lb n="0031c08"/>現。加持孔雀尾遙轉。欲夢中知一切事。<note n="0031028" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">三＋（時）【甲】</note><app n="0031028"><lem>三</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">三時</rdg></app>
<lb n="0031c09"/>念誦其夜見<note n="0031029" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔之〕－【甲】</note><app n="0031029"><lem>之</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>。又欲除惡夢者。以油麻護
<lb n="0031c10"/>摩。又欲止息口舌取雞翅翎護摩。若處子婆
<lb n="0031c11"/>&CB00344;&CB00610;淫女月帛護摩。悉<note n="0031030" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">&CB00085;＝縛【甲】</note><app n="0031030"><lem>&CB00085;</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">縛</rdg></app>始迦羅拏。若求一
<lb n="0031c12"/>切事應廣供養觀自在。八日一日夜不食念
<lb n="0031c13"/>誦滿一切願。又於觀自在菩薩前。三時時別
<lb n="0031c14"/>誦三遍。滿三月菩薩滿其所願。又於佛像前
<lb n="0031c15"/>三時時別誦三遍。滿三月佛滿其願</p></div1>
<lb n="0031c16"/><div1 type="pin"><mulu type="品" level="1" n="5" label="印品"/><head>印品</head>
<lb n="0031c17"/><p>合掌<note n="0031031" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">以＝已【甲】</note><app n="0031031"><lem>以</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">已</rdg></app>二水二風交地空各開&CB00594;。二火相合
<lb n="0031c18"/>是根本印。芙蓉合掌是為大蓮花印。不易大
<lb n="0031c19"/>蓮花開&CB00594;地空。是禳奪諸罪印。又外<note n="0031032" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔叉〕－【甲】</note><app n="0031032"><lem>叉</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>金剛
<lb n="0031c20"/>縛。合二風如蓮花葉。二空&CB00594;相逼是三昧<note n="0031033" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">印＝耶【甲】</note><app n="0031033"><lem>印</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">耶</rdg></app>。
<lb n="0031c21"/>又分二<note n="0031034" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">手＝羽【甲】</note><app n="0031034"><lem>手</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">羽</rdg></app>作蓮花拳。便以慧拳旋繞定拳。作
<lb n="0031c22"/>開八葉勢是羯磨印<note place="inline">請如來</note><note n="0031035" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">呬唎＝紇利【甲】</note><app n="0031035"><lem>呬唎</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">紇利</rdg></app><note place="inline">二合</note>字觀於心
<lb n="0031c23"/>月蓮。是法印。觀諸法如蓮花不著於水。諸法
<lb n="0031c24"/>亦然不染欲等。是智印。蓮花阿闍梨。欲授弟
<lb n="0031c25"/>子阿闍梨位。以蓮花授與弟子二掌中。又加
<lb n="0031c26"/>持蓮花鬘一千八遍。繫弟子頭上。加持</p>
<lb n="0031c27"/><p>真言曰</p>
<lb n="0031c28"/><p type="dharani">唵<anchor id="fxT20p0031c01"/><note place="inline">引</note>跛<anchor id="fxT20p0031c02"/>娜麼<note place="inline">二合</note>麼<note place="inline">引</note><note n="0031036" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">&CB00256;＝羅【甲】</note><app n="0031036"><lem>&CB00256;</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">羅</rdg></app><note place="inline">引</note>鼻詵<note n="0031037" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">左路引計濕＝者三魯計失【甲】</note><app n="0031037"><lem>左路<note place="inline">引</note>計
<lb n="0031c29"/>濕</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">者三魯計失</rdg></app>&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合</note><note n="0031038" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">囉＋（四）細註【甲】</note><app n="0031038"><lem>囉</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">囉<note place="inline">四</note></rdg></app>數<note n="0031039" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">索＋（五）細註【甲】</note><app n="0031039"><lem>索</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">索<note place="inline">五</note></rdg></app></p>
<pb ed="T" id="T20.1040.0032a" n="0032a"/>
<lb n="0032a01"/><p>由是得為蓮花部中阿闍梨。我今說蓮花部
<lb n="0032a02"/>修行禁戒儀。則先供養觀自在菩薩。應服一
<lb n="0032a03"/>掬遇牟怛囉若少分摩夷。即一切清淨。然觀
<lb n="0032a04"/>自身作觀自在菩薩。日誦一千遍乃至七日。
<lb n="0032a05"/>禁戒得成就。從此已後一切食一切處作。皆
<lb n="0032a06"/>不為污染。我今說普通一切供養儀。則二<note n="0032001" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔手〕－【甲】＊</note><app n="0032001"><lem>手</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>
<lb n="0032a07"/>為金剛拳。各安於腰側。向左小低頭。是為恭
<lb n="0032a08"/>敬禮。又二<anchor id="fxT20p0032a01"/>手從額分向後繫鬘勢。歷度下垂
<lb n="0032a09"/>帶。是為獻花鬘。又二<anchor id="fxT20p0032a02"/>手從於臍漸上至口
<lb n="0032a10"/>寫。是為獻歌詠。又二<anchor id="fxT20p0032a03"/>手從<note n="0032002" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔口〕－【甲】</note><app n="0032002"><lem>口</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>檀慧歷展相
<lb n="0032a11"/>旋遶上頂虛合掌。是獻金剛舞。由是供養如
<lb n="0032a12"/>來位尚不難得。況餘悉地。何以故。一切樂不
<lb n="0032a13"/>如此金剛薩埵故</p>
<lb n="0032a14"/><juan fun="close" n="001"><jhead>金剛頂<note n="0032003" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔經〕－【甲】</note><app n="0032003"><lem>經</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>降三世<note n="0032004" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔大〕－【甲】</note><app n="0032004"><lem>大</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>儀軌法<note n="0032005" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔王教…卷〕二十四字－【甲】</note><app n="0032005" word-count="24"><lem>王教中觀自
<lb n="0032a15"/>在菩薩心真言一切如來蓮花大曼拏&CB00256;品一
<lb n="0032a16"/>卷</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app></jhead></juan></div1>
</body></text></TEI.2>
